data.description: Sweet sweet super beautiful townhome available now in central Tucson  It is a rare offering in a small development.   Almost 2000 ft.!  Upstairs primary is to die for!  Downstairs living room boasts of a fireplace and high ceilings.  It leads to a very private patio with a spa! Close to Aqua Vida at Glenn & Country Club. Unbelievable placement in the neighborhood. Check it out now  New price!   Sellers shall accept or counter all offers received between 285-300000.00,
